OL,3,CEdinburgh University lecturers begin
OL,4,Cwalkout amid dispute over #140m cuts
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FLecturers and other staff at the
OL,8,FUniversity of Edinburgh are set to
OL,9,Fbegin a five-day walkout in a dispute
OL,10,Fover plans to cut #140 million from
OL,11,Fthe university's budget.
OL,13,FMembers of the University and College
OL,14,FUnion (UCU) are expected to be on
OL,15,Fpicket lines at various sites around
OL,16,Fthe university every day until Friday
OL,17,FSeptember 12.
OL,19,FA rally is also due to be held in the
OL,20,Fcity's George Square at 12pm on Monday.
