OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FThe union said its members had "no
OL,8,Fchoice" but to take industrial action
OL,9,Ffollowing the university's refusal to
OL,10,Frule out compulsory redundancies as
OL,11,Fpart of its savings bid, with as many
OL,12,Fas 1,800 jobs understood to be at risk.
OL,14,FIt also disputed the need for the cuts
OL,15,F` which it said are the "largest ever
OL,16,Fseen" in the history of Scottish
OL,17,Fhigher education ` due to the
OL,18,Funiversity not being in deficit.
