OL,7,FThe union added the university was
OL,8,F"one of the richest in the country",
OL,9,Fand said it could cut back on capital
OL,10,Fexpenditure and building work, or draw
OL,11,Fon its "large reserves", instead of
OL,12,Fcutting staff.
OL,14,FIn February, university principal
OL,15,FProfessor Sir Peter Mathieson said it
OL,16,Fneeded to achieve "a smaller staff
OL,17,Fbase and lower operating costs" within
OL,18,F18 months due to a forecast operating
OL,19,Fdeficit.
