OL,7,FThe walk-out coincides with the
OL,8,Funiversity's "welcome week", when new
OL,9,Fstudents arrive on campus for the
OL,10,Ffirst time.
OL,12,FUCU branch president Sophia Woodman
OL,13,Fsaid: "Students arriving this week on
OL,14,Fcampus and starting their university
OL,15,Fjourney should be able to be confident
OL,16,Fthat they'll complete their studies in
OL,17,Fa university that retains its current
OL,18,Freputation for excellence and that
OL,19,Foffers students the courses they
OL,20,Fsigned up for, as well as the support
OL,21,Fthey need to do well in their studies.
