OL,7,F"It's impossible, though, to cut 1,800
OL,8,Fstaff from any university without
OL,9,Fseriously impacting the teaching,
OL,10,Fresearch and student experience and
OL,11,Fdamaging the university's reputation.
OL,13,F"No-one wants to go on strike, but
OL,14,Fstaff are sounding the alarm about the
OL,15,Fimpact of these cuts.
