OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,F"Staff are striking because they have
OL,8,Fno choice but to take this week's
OL,9,Faction to force senior management to
OL,10,Fre-engage, to rule out the use of
OL,11,Fcompulsory redundancies and to end
OL,12,Fthis dispute."
OL,14,FThe action comes after a day of strike
OL,15,Faction on June 20, when UCU members
OL,16,Fwalked out during a university open
OL,17,Fday.
