OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,F"Instead of pressing on with cuts and
OL,8,Fjob losses Peter Mathieson needs to
OL,9,Flisten to staff at the university,
OL,10,Fengage with the union and commit to
OL,11,Fruling out the use of compulsory
OL,12,Fredundancies.
OL,14,F"Anything else is academic vandalism
OL,15,Fon an unprecedented scale."
OL,17,FThe university announced last week
OL,18,Fthat it has launched a new voluntary
OL,19,Fredundancy scheme for staff in senior
OL,20,Fgrades, along with an "enhanced"
OL,21,Fretirement scheme for employees.
